lead_paragraph: Slovakia coach Jan Kozak is refusing to accept that Gareth Bale-led Wales are a one-man team ahead of their Euro 2016 opener, although he is well aware of the forward's threat.

headline.print_headline: Wales Not Just About Bale, Says Kozak
headline.main: Wales Not Just About Bale, Says Kozak
